.DT
add_follower
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_follower

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_follower -  This method adds a follower to the living object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_follower(object ob)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object to follow us
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a follower to the living object.  A follower will
happily follow around the person in front.  Used in the follow
command.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
remove_follower(), query_followers()
.EP

